sub_sections.text:
Non-compliance or irregularity for not applying 10 (ten) thousand taka only
for registration or enlistment within the
prescribed time-limit;

Non-compliance or irregularity for not 10 (ten) thousand taka only
displaying the registration or turnover tax
certificate in a visible place;

Non-compliance or irregularity for not 10 (ten) thousand taka only
informing the Commissioner of the change in
the information of the economic activity;

Non-compliance or irregularity for not filing the 10 (ten) thousand taka only
VAT or turnover tax return within the prescribed
time period;

Non-compliance or irregularity for not issuing 10 (ten) thousand taka only
tax invoice, credit note, debit note, combined
tax invoice and withholding certificate;
